# Supabase & Data

## Clients

- Server routes / Server Actions: `createClient()` from `utils/supabase/server.ts`
- Client components: `utils/supabase/client.ts`
- Webhooks / admin: service role only where RLS must be bypassed

## Patterns

- Bulk single-flight inserts for multi-row data (slides, captions)
- Realtime subscriptions for async assets (images, captions, exports) — avoid client polling-only UX
- RLS: users see only their own campaigns, brands, connections

## Migrations

- Filename: `supabase/migrations/YYYYMMDDHHMMSS_description.sql`
- Apply to production before deploying code that depends on new columns
- Billing tier caps live in `apply_tier_entitlement()` — keep in sync with `utils/plan-limits.ts`

## Key tables

`campaigns`, `slides`, `slide_images`, `platform_captions`, `platform_connections`, `platform_posts`, `usage_balances`, `usage_events`, `brands`, `exports`
